data.description:
ASSUMABLE LOAN WITH 3.25% INTEREST RATE FOR QUALIFIED BUYERS!
Remarkable home in the sought after Johnson Ranch community of San Tan Valley. Entering the home you will be greeted with modern tile flooring that spreads throughout the home accompanied by new carpets in each room. Kitchen features brand new cabinets, Quartz countertops and an added eat-in breakfast.  Deep drawers for all of your storage needs.  Both bathrooms share the Quartz countertop. When you make your way to the backyard you will not only find no neighbors behind, the grand feature will be the play pool of your dreams with newly restored pool equipment.
